---
title  : LongFish
summary: Documentation format stylized after ruby-lang.org

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer

description:
  LongFish is RDoc template modeled after John Long's design
  the ruby-lang.org. It allows your Ruby application or library
  have a very Ruby look and feel.

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/longfish
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/longfish

requires:
  - clap
  - rdazzle
  - syckle (build)

